Author: Zaoqu Liu [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0452-742X>)
Maintainer: Zaoqu Liu <liuzaoqu@163.com>
Description: Comprehensive database of 7,665 genetic perturbation RNA-seq datasets 
    covering 2,810 genes across 1,063 cell lines and 71 tissue types, aggregated into 
    18.9 million gene-gene relationships (826K high-confidence). Provides intelligent 
    query functions for gene regulatory network analysis, pathway analysis, and drug 
    target prediction. Optimized for LLM agent integration with natural language-friendly 
    interfaces. Combines SQLite for millisecond queries and qs format for raw data access.
